{"author":{"id":"b78c39e7b13f90a5827abfba043255fe7a4ede1499df23f110fffe5abfa44adc"},"ops":[{"type":1,"timestamp":1769542449,"nonce":"RxDALmwb1M1OUyxe8oG2kafh1Ic=","metadata":{"github-id":"I_kwDOQ241x87mMz8d","github-url":"https://github.com/rolker/ros2_agent_workspace/issues/74","origin":"github"},"title":"[System] Enforce AI Signature in Skills and Workflows","message":"### Description\nSeveral skills and workflows instruct agents to create GitHub Issues or Pull Requests but fail to explicitly require the mandatory AI Signature defined in `.agent/rules/common/ai-signature.md`.\n\n### Affected Files\n- `.agent/skills/issue-triage/SKILL.md` (Issue creation)\n- `.agent/skills/agent-optimization/SKILL.md` (Issue creation)\n- `.agent/workflows/dev/submit-pr.md` (PR creation)\n\n### Proposed Solution\nUpdate these files to explicitly instruct agents to append the signature:\n```markdown\n\n---\n**🤖 Authored-By**: `\u003cAgent Name\u003e`\n```\n\n### Labels\n`system-improvement`, `compliance`\n\n---\n**🤖 Authored-By**: `Gemini CLI Agent`","files":null}]}